data.description: Contract Pending This one is a must see! Check out this beautifully updated brick ranch home with 2 stall attached garage on a huge lot at the end of a cul-de-sac! The main level boasts high quality LVP flooring throughout. You'll love the large updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances and a walk-in pantry! There are 3 bedrooms on the main level, including a big primary bedroom with a 3/4 bath attached! The living room, informal dining area, and full bath complete the main level. In the basement you'll find a mostly finished space with a large family room, rec room, 4th bedroom, additional 3/4 bath, and laundry area. Added bonus - a 15" x 14" workshop area and plenty storage space. The electrical panel has also been updated! The back yard is sure to amaze with a large fenced in lot, deck with pergola, fire-pit area, playset, and landscaping with curbed edging! All you need to do is move in and make it your home-sweet-home before someone else does!
